---
import Section from '../layout/Section.astro';
---

<Section id="contact" background="cream">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 xl:px-16 py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24">
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16 fade-in-up">
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-black uppercase mb-6 md:mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Contáctanos
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-center mb-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-dark fade-in-up leading-relaxed px-4" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
        ¿Tienes preguntas? Estamos aquí para ayudarte. 
        Contáctanos y te responderemos lo antes posible.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid Principal -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16 mb-12 md:mb-16">
      
      <!-- Card de Contacto Principal -->
      <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow via-orange to-pink border-[4px] border-black shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] p-6 md:p-8 transform hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px] hover:shadow-[10px_10px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Ilustración decorativa -->
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 opacity-20 pointer-events-none">
            <img src="/dolfin.png" alt="" class="w-24 h-24 md:w-32 md:h-32 sprite-float" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h3 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-2 text-black uppercase leading-tight drop-shadow-[2px_2px_0px_rgba(255,255,255,0.3)]">
              Angelo Franco
            </h3>
            <p class="font-heading text-lg md:text-xl mb-8 text-black font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">
              Coordinador del Festival
            </p>

            <!-- Botones de Contacto -->
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <a
                href="https://wa.me/593969310187"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="bg-black text-white-warm px-6 py-4 border-[3px] border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-center min-h-[56px] flex items-center justify-center gap-3 hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px] active:translate-x-[4px] active:translate-y-[4px] active:shadow-[2px_2px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] transition-all"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-phone"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
                WhatsApp: +593 96 931 0187
              </a>

              <a
                href="mailto:sanmateolongfestival@gmail.com"
                class="bg-white-warm text-black px-6 py-4 border-[3px] border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-center min-h-[56px] flex items-center justify-center gap-3 hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px] active:translate-x-[4px] active:translate-y-[4px] active:shadow-[2px_2px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] transition-all"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-mail"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
                sanmateolongfestival@gmail.com
              </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Horario de Atención -->
            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t-2 border-black/30">
              <p class="font-heading text-sm md:text-base font-bold mb-3 text-black uppercase tracking-wide">
                ⏰ Horario de Atención
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-2 font-body text-sm md:text-base text-black">
                <p class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="font-bold">Lunes a Viernes:</span>
                  <span>9am - 6pm</span>
                </p>
                <p class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="font-bold">Sábados:</span>
                  <span>9am - 1pm</span>
                </p>
                <p class="flex items-center gap-2 mt-3">
                  <span class="text-orange font-bold">✓</span>
                  <span>Respuesta en 24 horas</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Redes Sociales -->
      <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.25s;">
        <div class="bg-white-warm border-[4px] border-black shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] p-6 md:p-8 h-full flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-6 text-black uppercase leading-tight text-center">
            Síguenos en<br />Redes Sociales
          </h3>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6 flex-grow">
            <a 
              href="https://www.instagram.com/sanmateolongboardfestival" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink to-orange border-[3px] border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] p-4 text-center transform hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px] hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] transition-all flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 min-h-[120px]"
            >
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-instagram text-white-warm"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"/></svg>
              <span class="font-heading text-sm font-bold text-white-warm uppercase tracking-wide">Instagram</span>
            </a>
            
            <a 
              href="https://www.facebook.com/sanmateolongboardfestival" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="bg-blue-600 border-[3px] border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] p-4 text-center transform hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px] hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] transition-all flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 min-h-[120px]"
            >
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-facebook text-white-warm"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
              <span class="font-heading text-sm font-bold text-white-warm uppercase tracking-wide">Facebook</span>
            </a>
            
            <a 
              href="#" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="bg-black border-[3px] border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] p-4 text-center transform hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px] hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] transition-all flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 min-h-[120px]"
            >
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-music text-white-warm"><circle cx="12" cy="18" r="4"/><path d="M6 18V4l12-2v14"/></svg>
              <span class="font-heading text-sm font-bold text-white-warm uppercase tracking-wide">TikTok</span>
            </a>
            
            <a 
              href="#" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="bg-sky-500 border-[3px] border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] p-4 text-center transform hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px] hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] transition-all flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 min-h-[120px]"
            >
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-twitter text-white-warm"><path d="M22 4s-.7 2.1-2 3.4c1.6 10-9.4 17.3-18 11.6 2.2.1 4.4-.6 6-2C3 15.5.5 9.6 3 5c2.2 2.6 5.6 4.1 9 4-.9-4.2 4-6.6 7-3.8 1.1 0 3-1.2 3-1.2z"/></svg>
              <span class="font-heading text-sm font-bold text-white-warm uppercase tracking-wide">Twitter</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-yellow/30 border-2 border-black p-4 text-center">
            <p class="font-heading text-xs md:text-sm font-bold text-black uppercase tracking-wide">
              #SanMateoLongFest #LongFest2025 #SurfEcuador
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Rápido -->
    <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
      <div class="bg-white-warm border-[4px] border-black shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] p-6 md:p-8">
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-8 text-black uppercase leading-tight text-center">
          Preguntas<br />Frecuentes
        </h3>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
          <div class="border-2 border-black p-4 md:p-5 bg-yellow/20">
            <p class="font-heading text-base md:text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black uppercase">
              ¿Puedo inscribirme en el lugar?
            </p>
            <p class="font-body text-sm md:text-base text-black leading-relaxed">
              Sí, pero recomendamos pre-inscripción online para asegurar tu plaza.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-2 border-black p-4 md:p-5 bg-orange/20">
            <p class="font-heading text-base md:text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black uppercase">
              ¿Hay límite de edad?
            </p>
            <p class="font-body text-sm md:text-base text-black leading-relaxed">
              Cada categoría tiene sus requisitos. Niños desde 8 años con autorización.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-2 border-black p-4 md:p-5 bg-pink/20">
            <p class="font-heading text-base md:text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black uppercase">
              ¿Puedo participar en múltiples categorías?
            </p>
            <p class="font-body text-sm md:text-base text-black leading-relaxed">
              No, solo una categoría por persona para dar oportunidad a todos.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-2 border-black p-4 md:p-5 bg-yellow/20">
            <p class="font-heading text-base md:text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black uppercase">
              ¿Qué pasa si el clima no acompaña?
            </p>
            <p class="font-body text-sm md:text-base text-black leading-relaxed">
              Tenemos días de reserva. Mantendremos informados por redes sociales.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t-2 border-black/20 text-center">
          <a 
            href="#info" 
            class="inline-block bg-black text-white-warm px-6 py-3 border-[3px] border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-wide hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px] active:translate-x-[4px] active:translate-y-[4px] active:shadow-[2px_2px_0px_0px_rgba(26,26,26,1)] transition-all"
          >
            Ver Todas las Preguntas Frecuentes
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
